{"tid":1924101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有間黃鞋舖頂唔順了","createTime":"2020-03-13T12:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T10:09:05.000Z","uid":60205,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8f9d252d5da1031cd7ae0ac408c02f91081a48","tid":1924101,"uid":60205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:57:36.000Z","msg":"間鞋舖係中環環球大廈三樓361 <br />\n<br />\n老闆由上年6月社運開始都已有參與 由於舖位係中環呢9個月影響都好大 但佢當然無鬧過同路人同學生一句 仲不時係舖頭一邊睇新聞一邊屌鳩popo 如果附近有示威 亦有直接落樓下屌popo <br />\n<br />\n但我就睇住佢生意大跌 業主又好似唔多肯減租 宜家終於頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n老細做埋呢兩日（14同15）就關門大吉 話當休息下先 佢主力賣啲婆仔鞋同女裝波鞋 （因為佢主要客源係賓賓） 大多一舊水以下就有交易 希望你地幫下佢清一清貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：附近商戶"},{"pid":"7ac8e173e5934309729c9b5edc70120eb97f64b3","tid":1924101,"uid":17261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"名？賣咩類型嘅鞋？"},{"pid":"2cdf3b6b308e9f2f10118f26a0115b2a7e9f930b","tid":1924101,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:03:18.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6b681b20564939a9ec6dda90e78b422a2814b6","tid":1924101,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188b2084c88e0d98d3d462eae77c02bf98722808","tid":1924101,"uid":3534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:09:46.000Z","msg":"名"},{"pid":"36940da82c45eeaedd0883a4ab36c1d6781233cf","tid":1924101,"uid":60205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:34:48.000Z","msg":"名好似係wavy shoes"},{"pid":"7e611b8940e9180201218c2b5495307f8e353ce2","tid":1924101,"uid":28003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:08:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d50742a57ec4ebe8708b0c8d1f443168d6abb9d5","tid":1924101,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":